text: The Tour of Antalya is a multi-day road cycling race held annually in Turkey. It is part of UCI Europe Tour in category 2.1. The first two editions were however only in category 2.2, before upgrading in 2020.. ==Winners== ==References== Category:Cycle races in Turkey Category:2018 establishments in Turkey Category:Recurring sporting events established in 2018 Category:UCI Europe Tour races
